  "summary": "gpt-chat-cli exfiltrates host and filesystem data to attacker-controlled C2",
  "details": "The package's collect.js gathers host identity (os.hostname(), os.homedir()) and filesystem reconnaissance via fs.existsSync, leverages child_process, and POSTs the collected data over HTTP to the hardcoded attacker-controlled endpoint http://aab.sportsontheweb.net. The combination of os/host enumeration, filesystem probing, and a hardcoded non-publisher exfiltration destination is a credential/host-data stealer pattern. Installing or loading this package causes the installer's machine identity and local filesystem signals to be sent to the attacker.",
